      "content": "ugh just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. its kinda hurting a lot and i cant really walk on it right now. think i just need to do some RICE (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a few days and it'll be fine? i really dont wanna go to the clinic if i dont have to",
