      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it's definitely pretty swollen. do you think i should probably try to walk on it a bit today just to see if it's getting better, or should i just stay off it completely? and how much ibuprofen should i actually take to keep the swelling down? i have a bottle of 400mg ones here.",
